## рџЏ—пёЏ Architecture

```
pykworldsim/
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ core/
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ entity.py          Thread-safe entity ID allocation
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ world.py           ECS container: entities + components + systems
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ simulation.py      Deterministic, pausable simulation loop
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ components/
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ position.py    2-D spatial coordinate
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ velocity.py    2-D velocity vector
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ person.py      Individual agent (age, health, happiness, energy)
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ location.py    Named place / city
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ relationship.py Directed bond between entities
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ job.py         Occupation / role
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ goal.py        Motivation / objective
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ event.py       Scheduled time-based occurrence
в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ systems/
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ base_system.py Abstract base class
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ movement.py    pos += vel Г— dt
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ physics.py     Gravity + boundary bouncing
в”‚   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ social.py      Ageing, energy, happiness, goal progress
в”‚   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ event.py       Event scheduling and dispatch
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ config/
в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ loader.py      YAML / JSON в†’ World + Simulation
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ plugins/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ registry.py        Dynamic system registration
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ utils/
в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ logging.py         Logging configuration helper
в””в”Ђв”Ђ cli.py                 Typer CLI with Rich output
```

**ECS pattern:**

| Concept | Role |
|---|---|
| **Entity** | Opaque integer ID вЂ” carries no data |
| **Component** | Plain dataclass вЂ” data only, no logic |
| **System** | Logic only вЂ” queries entities by component, mutates them |

